As per the provisions therein Maharashtra Government Servants Regulation of Transfers and Prevention of Delay in Discharge of Official Duties Act, 2005, with the approval of Competent Authority, the officers in Indian Forest Service were promoted vide Government order dated 12.02.2025 referred above.
